   "source": [
    "# MetaPulsar Custom PTA Configuration Tutorial\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook demonstrates how to add custom PTA configurations and use them in the MetaPulsar workflow.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Learning Objectives\n",
    "- Understand PTA configuration structure\n",
    "- Learn how to add custom PTAs to the discovery service\n",
    "- Explore custom PTA integration with MetaPulsar\n",
    "- Handle custom PTA file patterns and settings\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
